    <h2>🎉 Welcome to Skilledustore!</h2>
    
    <p>Hello <strong>${name}</strong>,</p>
    
    <p>Thank you for joining Skilledustore! We're thrilled to have you as part of our group-buy learning community. Get ready to access 80+ premium learning tools at the lowest price!</p>
    
    <div class="highlight-box">
      <h3>🔑 Activate Your Account</h3>
      <p>To complete your registration and unlock your group-buy access, please activate your account using the secure code below:</p>
      
      <div style="text-align: center; margin: 25px 0;">
        <div style="display: inline-block; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8f9fa 0%, #e9ecef 100%); border: 2px dashed #667eea; font-size: 32px; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 8px; padding: 20px 40px; border-radius: 12px; color: #495057; font-family: 'Courier New', monospace; box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.1);">
          ${activationCode}
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <p style="text-align: center; color: #6c757d; font-size: 14px;">
