      <ul style="color: #495057; line-height: 1.8; padding-left: 20px;">
        <li>Access 80+ premium tools — Udemy, Coursera, LinkedIn Learning & more</li>
        <li>Save up to 80% compared to retail pricing</li>
        <li>Instant access after payment — no waiting</li>
        <li>Earn verified certificates upon course completion</li>
        <li>18/7 dedicated support via WhatsApp</li>
        <li>Access from any device, anywhere</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    
    <div class="info-card">
      <h4>💡 Success Tips</h4>
      <ul style="color: #495057; line-height: 1.8; padding-left: 20px;">
