        📚 Explore Tools
      </a>
    </div>
    
    <p style="color: #6c757d; font-size: 14px; text-align: center; margin-top: 20px;">
      Having trouble? You can also manually enter the code: <strong>${activationCode}</strong>
    </p>
    
